    Colors are legitemely stolen from https://github.com/navarasu/onedark.nvim/blob/master/lua/onedark/palette.lua#L142-L169.
    Download bemoji script at  and place it at .local/bin if you wanna the menu to display on Super+grave keypress.
    The i3 config uses
    - bemoji: https://github.com/marty-oehme/bemoji
    - xsecurelock: available at your usual repository, i guess
    - some dmenu scripts i have in .local/bin
    - and boomer: https://github.com/tsoding/boomer. Allows you to zoom into and focus on smth during a stream, really handy.
